{"tid":2332163,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★大陸航空公司要求核酸證明用正確名稱「新冠肺炎」，「武漢肺炎」會被視為無效","createTime":"2020-12-19T11:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T09:37:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4368d6cceffe26813ae5eaf6b88cf5b2d07a73","tid":2332163,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:32:33.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】大陸多間航空公司發通告，兩岸航線的旅客出示的核酸檢測證明，如非使用正確名稱「新冠肺炎」，會被拒入境。<br />\n<br />\n南方航空的通告指，世界衛生組織已發布對於新冠肺炎的正名，旅客要注意醫療機構提供的核酸檢測證明書，如非正確名稱將被拒入境。<br />\n<br />\n台灣中央社報道，國航及深航向旅行社發通告指，如果檢測報告出現「武漢肺炎」會被視為無效。報道指，台灣醫療機構發出的檢測報告一般註明「2019冠狀病毒疾病」或「COVID-19」字樣，大陸規定兩岸航班乘客必須出示72小時內核酸檢測陰性證明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=417187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417187&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWP7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=c5a17cd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417187&h=f8f06e81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=417187</a>"},{"pid":"adb511a06b341f876ea67c50cbfab6ea11cb735b","tid":2332163,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:32:56.000Z","msg":"支肺呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f24855ade49d29ec176a15812c7bd904c67c8e2","tid":2332163,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:34:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">中國肺炎</span>"},{"pid":"a2e19c9a1600bb2200814a9e2c32935491eb8682","tid":2332163,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">多尻餘</span>"},{"pid":"646f56824fdbf06f1e99c0eeb51bc9e1a5880f51","tid":2332163,"uid":86509,"